{"tid":1777347,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"守港鐵站打記者 兩藍絲被捕","createTime":"2019-12-10T06:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T07:27:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"74484920aeb2b1f147efc5c2e3fb74bd8ee89b4a","tid":1777347,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T06:58:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191210/6KEHGNQPQQ44HMVB6VQNVM3ALI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191210%2F6KEHGNQPQQ44HMVB6VQNVM3ALI%2F&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cTQSOVv8pHkqsyXWJi2kweQ%3D&h=b56f0130\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191210%2F6KEHGNQPQQ44HMVB6VQNVM3ALI%2F&h=92c9ebeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191210/6KEHGNQPQQ44HMVB6VQNVM3ALI/</a><br />\n<br />\n守港鐵站打記者 兩藍絲被捕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】兩批「藍絲」昨晨分別在港鐵黃大仙站及屯門站「反三罷」，與阻礙列車車門運作的示威者對罵，並挑釁在場採訪的記者，其中在黃大仙站，一名《壹週刊》記者在月台拍攝採訪時，遭一批藍絲打傷手及拍爛攝錄機，警方事後拘捕兩名涉案男女。<br />\n<br />\n昨晨7時20分， 一批帶口罩疑為「藍絲」的男女，帶同雨傘遊走黃大仙站月台，協助警方阻止抗爭者阻礙列車運作。其間一名《壹週刊》記者在月台拍攝時，五名戴口罩男女包圍記者並阻礙拍攝，有人企圖搶奪記者攝影器材，糾纏期間記者分別遭一名54歲盧姓男子及一名21歲黃姓女子以手襲擊及從後推撞，記者手腕受傷，攝錄機損毀，送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191210/large/1575909485_e455.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191210%2Flarge%2F1575909485_e455.jpg&h=3985de15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【黃大仙】一批戴口罩藍絲昨在月台推撞記者，事後一名金毛盧姓男子被警員帶走。劉柏麟攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n防暴到場 施襲者照兇人<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：萬六槍彈攻大學「如戰爭狀態」<br />\n<br />\n一批防暴警接報到場，其間口罩男女仍不時兇記者，「你係咩記者，你係咪想俾人私了？」又對記者粗言穢語，警員調查後，以涉嫌普通襲擊及刑事毀壞拘捕盧，另以涉嫌普通襲擊拘捕黃，案件由黃大仙警區刑事調查隊第四隊跟進。《壹週刊》發聲明譴責暴徒針對記者行使暴力，妨礙香港新聞自由，指不容任何人以暴力干擾記者的採訪工作，使香港蒙上暴力恐嚇陰影，《壹週刊》保留對暴徒的一切追究權利。<br />\n<br />\n另外，昨晨7時半，屯門站月台亦有數名「藍絲大媽」到場「維持秩序」，並指罵抗爭者阻人上班，當有人阻礙列車就起哄，並出手阻止，其間又與記者口角，並舉機拍攝記者。<br />\n<br />\n■記者劉柏麟、張家豪"},{"pid":"6855bd85fec548db76dcb5bf1e45208cde8fa18d","tid":1777347,"uid":224066,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:03:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XGcwGXB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXGcwGXB.jpg&h=d793352f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f290adcc1975e1d3a3c3c452fd6d8478e7edbe6","tid":1777347,"uid":169665,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:05:11.000Z","msg":"返去警署飲杯茶, 講聲辛苦哂咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eacdcae8ecdd2d378b598a1607286a88e146886","tid":1777347,"uid":56731,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:08:47.000Z","msg":"被捕後即放人"},{"pid":"b43a0fea999daf5e35dd00ab602ee9424dadf55c","tid":1777347,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:11:07.000Z","msg":"記者真係好重要 , 毓民仲話叫記者罷工 , 唔知咩心態 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa89d2dd497c2d78c08cc0f51c11c20791be1ee2","tid":1777347,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:11:59.000Z","msg":"死金毛方死人唔認得你咩"},{"pid":"b330df87d8e9b033553da3dd0098fba3791d4e68","tid":1777347,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b43a0fea999daf5e35dd00ab602ee9424dadf55c","tid":1777347,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:11:07.000Z","msg":"記者真係好重要 , 毓民仲話叫記者罷工 , 唔知咩心態 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:12:07.000Z","msg":"又一個盲撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed1920a1db531bc47cb1834a69a232693c50d1d0","tid":1777347,"uid":37058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:17:06.000Z","msg":"好快放返"},{"pid":"806d9171b299a2ee0681e7679417e3312c27bc86","tid":1777347,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:27:09.000Z","msg":"Cosplay示威者<img s